data.title: EuroBasket 2013 Quarterfinals Preview
data.meta_description: Back in his home country of Slovenia, Suns' point guard Goran Dragic has led Slovenia to the quartefinals of EuroBasket 2013, which begin on Wednesday. They're joined by seven other teams, which include everything from perennial powerhouses like Spain to tournament surprises like Ukraine. Here's a look at the best of each team's talent, and how they used that talent to get this far.
